  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 cups of vegetable oil in a large, deep pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the grated ginger and minced garlic and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in the red curry paste and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the coconut milk, vegetable broth, fish-free bouillon cubes, and brown sugar. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10-12 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened.",
    "Stir in the myeongnan-roe and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, until heated through.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "To flambé the dish, carefully ignite the mixture with a match or lighter, allowing the flames to cook for 30 seconds to 1 minute.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve immediately."
  ],
